<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.9">
<l>iṉṉā reṉṟaṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>aṉṉē yāḻiyoṭum</l>
<l>poṉṉār cārṅkamu ṭaiyava ṭikaḷai</l>
<l>iṉṉā reṉṟaṟiyēṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I didn’t know of such a person;</l>
<l>Oh, my! A god with a golden Sārnga [bow]</l>
<l>As well as a discus,</l>
<l>I didn’t know of such a person!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
